          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Companies benefit when they create messaging that highlights that they’re different.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It helps them win clients, attract investors, and captivate potential hirees.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The problem is that most companies often say the same thing, only differently. Some variation of ‘we're the best, for reasons X, Y, Z.’",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "That’s not differentiation. It’s ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "reiteration",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ".",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "No. The way to communicate you’re different ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "isn’t",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " to tell the same story, in a new way. It’s to tell a different story (a better one) altogether.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
